title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Familiarity and routine can stifle your creativity and hamper your productivity even with the simplest of tasks. You yearn for change but might be unsure of how to invoke it now. Commit to altering your course of action rather than stubbornly trying to stick to the tried-and-true path of the past. The truth is an unconventional route can lead to time-consuming detours or wrong turns today. Nevertheless, overcoming your fear of failure may be required in order to successfully evolve. Poet T.S. Eliot wrote, Only those who will risk going too far can possibly find out how far one can go. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
